Jake Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jake_Thomas 0 Jake Thomas (born January 30, 1990) is an American actor, perhaps best known for his role as Matt McGuire, the title character's younger brother, in the Disney Channel show Lizzie McGuire (2001–04). In 2002, he won a Young Artist Award for supporting actor for his performance in A.I. Artificial Intelligence (2001). He also appeared in Cory in the House (2007–08), playing the role of Jason Stickler.
